WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 2=

01:54.260 --> 01:55.540
My Fengfu acupoint is sealed.

01:56.820 --> 01:57.740
I can't move.

02:03.330 --> 02:04.270
Your poison flared up?

02:04.770 --> 02:05.610
No.

02:10.220 --> 02:11.290
Are you afraid of the dark?

02:13.630 --> 02:14.480
Don't be.

02:14.500 --> 02:15.340
I'm not afraid.

02:16.980 --> 02:17.820
This is a box.

02:18.850 --> 02:19.880
They didn't harm us

02:19.880 --> 02:20.920
while we were unconscious.

02:20.960 --> 02:22.500
They probably want to capture us alive.

02:22.500 --> 02:23.410
Who are they?

02:23.716 --> 02:25.036
Why do they want to capture you?

02:25.380 --> 02:26.820
Shouldn't that be asked to you?

02:27.613 --> 02:29.037
Those who can reach Qingque Sect

02:29.685 --> 02:30.809
should be from the Six Sects.

02:35.660 --> 02:36.500
Ning,

02:37.173 --> 02:38.170
turn your head a little.

02:38.940 --> 02:39.780
What?

02:41.340 --> 02:42.190
What are you doing?

02:42.220 --> 02:43.153
Releasing your acupoint.

02:46.690 --> 02:47.610
I'll count to three.

02:48.340 --> 02:49.380
We'll rush out together.

02:49.500 --> 02:50.340
Okay.

02:50.450 --> 02:51.290
One,

02:51.980 --> 02:52.820
two,

02:52.890 --> 02:53.730
three.

03:08.220 --> 03:09.060
Careful.

03:29.540 --> 03:30.610
Chang Ning!

03:39.730 --> 03:40.730
Let go,

03:40.890 --> 03:42.130
or we'll all die.

03:42.980 --> 03:44.780
Halfway is the worst way,

03:44.911 --> 03:46.060
especially when saving lives.

03:49.060 --> 03:50.100
Help!

03:50.290 --> 03:51.850
Master!

03:52.610 --> 03:53.660
If no one comes,

03:54.100 --> 03:55.450
we'll die!

04:04.450 --> 04:06.450
Zhao, hold the rope!

04:22.980 --> 04:23.820
Zhao,

04:24.370 --> 04:25.210
what happened?

04:26.896 --> 04:28.266
Someone is trying to capture Ning.

04:29.490 --> 04:30.330
Chang.

04:31.660 --> 04:32.500
Chang Ning.

04:45.730 --> 04:46.570
Don't worry.

04:46.730 --> 04:47.570
He's fine.

04:48.100 --> 04:48.940
He'll wake up soon.

04:49.750 --> 04:50.600
Zhao,

04:50.610 --> 04:51.610
are your hands okay?

04:52.370 --> 04:53.210
I'm fine.

04:53.900 --> 04:56.140
Xingjia got anxious
and wrapped extra rounds.

04:56.660 --> 04:57.730
It's all my fault.

04:58.050 --> 04:58.980
I failed to protect you.

05:00.250 --> 05:01.250
The villains are bold.

05:01.930 --> 05:02.780
Not your fault.

05:04.540 --> 05:05.380
But Master,

05:05.730 --> 05:07.610
how did the people in black get here?

05:07.660 --> 05:09.170
Even flying birds can't do that.

05:09.930 --> 05:11.490
Could this be the same people

05:11.660 --> 05:13.210
who massacred Chang Fort?

05:14.290 --> 05:16.580
The Jianghu has been peaceful for years.

05:17.020 --> 05:18.220
We let our guard down.

05:18.810 --> 05:19.660
Now,

05:19.850 --> 05:21.780
we must stay alert.

05:26.140 --> 05:26.980
Yunke,

05:27.140 --> 05:28.050
I found several bodies

05:28.220 --> 05:29.540
in Qingque Town.

05:30.220 --> 05:32.050
The culprit disguised themselves

05:32.290 --> 05:33.310
as Guangtian Sect guards.

05:34.580 --> 05:35.420
Master,

05:35.610 --> 05:36.610
it's my fault.

05:37.220 --> 05:38.780
I'll go to pursue the culprit.

05:39.490 --> 05:40.716
They first massacred Chang Fort

05:41.730 --> 05:44.100
and then barged in here to silence Ning.

05:44.100 --> 05:45.386
This can only be the demon sect.

05:46.250 --> 05:48.100
The Patriarch's ritual is imminent.

05:48.250 --> 05:49.610
We can't have another riot.

05:50.460 --> 05:51.300
From today,

05:51.580 --> 05:54.540
strengthen the internal
and external gates' guard.

05:54.986 --> 05:56.170
Everyone going up the mountain

05:56.290 --> 05:57.170
must be checked.

05:57.490 --> 05:58.330
No negligence.

05:58.580 --> 05:59.420
- Yes.
- Yes.

06:07.220 --> 06:08.060
Zhao.

06:09.220 --> 06:10.580
The Siqi Sect is too weak.

06:10.660 --> 06:11.950
She couldn't even stand one move.

06:12.220 --> 06:13.089
My foundation is weak.

06:13.100 --> 06:14.469
It has nothing to do with the sect.

06:14.540 --> 06:15.380
Xiaolan,

06:15.427 --> 06:17.240
you didn't eat breakfast
this morning, right?

06:17.453 --> 06:18.900
So, you don't have enough strength.

06:19.050 --> 06:19.890
Lingbo,

06:20.370 --> 06:21.810
I'll take Xiaolan to find some food.

06:22.290 --> 06:23.130
Let's go.

06:23.290 --> 06:24.130
Cai Zhao,

06:25.580 --> 06:27.660
it seems your hand has healed.

06:30.290 --> 06:31.130
Yes.

06:32.050 --> 06:33.050
Thanks for your concern.

06:33.460 --> 06:34.300
Let's go.

06:34.730 --> 06:35.580
Zhuo!

06:47.700 --> 06:48.760
(Ding Zhuo)
I'm Ding Zhuo.

06:48.773 --> 06:50.930
Channeling inner power
into the weapon.

06:51.020 --> 06:51.900
So powerful.

06:52.220 --> 06:53.340
This is Zhuo.

06:53.660 --> 06:54.873
He just emerged from seclusion.

06:54.980 --> 06:55.820
Cai Zhao.

06:56.490 --> 06:57.330
Hi, Zhuo.

06:57.330 --> 06:58.200
Zhuo.

07:01.490 --> 07:02.330
May I spar with you?

07:05.100 --> 07:05.940
Zhao,

07:06.220 --> 07:08.020
Zhuo is obsessed with martial arts.

07:08.050 --> 07:08.900
Whenever he spars,

07:08.900 --> 07:10.540
he fights until one can't stand.

07:11.170 --> 07:12.140
Don't spar with him.

07:12.780 --> 07:13.620
What?

07:14.930 --> 07:15.770
Are you afraid?

07:17.140 --> 07:17.980
Sure. Let's spar.

07:19.460 --> 07:20.300
I'm ready.

07:23.700 --> 07:24.540
Zhuo,

07:24.610 --> 07:25.450
you've lost.

07:28.460 --> 07:29.660
Cai Zhao, you cheated.

07:29.900 --> 07:31.490
Lingbo, you can't wrong me.

07:32.490 --> 07:33.660
I didn't use hidden weapons

07:33.980 --> 07:35.020
or attack from behind.

07:35.580 --> 07:36.420
How did I cheat?

07:36.540 --> 07:38.100
But it hasn't even started.

07:38.460 --> 07:40.050
Martial contests are fatal struggles.

07:40.050 --> 07:40.906
At a critical moment,

07:40.917 --> 07:42.290
do we need to bathe, burn incense,

07:42.290 --> 07:43.730
and beat drums before starting?

07:44.220 --> 07:46.340
No wonder I was ambushed
a few days ago.

07:46.580 --> 07:48.100
It must have been because everyone

07:48.100 --> 07:49.250
weren't prepared.

07:49.250 --> 07:50.090
I...

07:53.460 --> 07:54.340
I admit defeat.

07:55.340 --> 07:56.180
Zhuo...

07:56.540 --> 07:57.940
Thank you, Zhuo.

07:59.540 --> 08:00.380
Xiaolan.

08:03.580 --> 08:04.420
Cai Zhao,

08:05.220 --> 08:06.250
just you wait.

08:09.100 --> 08:12.693
(Double Lotus Palace)

08:12.704 --> 08:14.737
It's said that the previous lord,
Yin Dai, had only

08:16.460 --> 08:18.170
two daughters, Qinglian and Sulian.

08:18.980 --> 08:19.980
Thus, it's named

08:20.610 --> 08:21.930
Double Lotus Palace.

08:22.730 --> 08:24.220
Though it lacks grandeur,

08:24.900 --> 08:26.170
it is elegant and extraordinary,

08:26.540 --> 08:27.610
stunningly beautiful.

08:30.370 --> 08:31.410
The tiles are fragile,

08:31.610 --> 08:33.490
transported from the Western Regions

08:34.010 --> 08:35.060
without damage.

08:36.300 --> 08:37.340
Truly priceless.

08:38.693 --> 08:39.940
Qingque Sect has always valued

08:39.940 --> 08:40.820
strict cultivation

08:41.460 --> 08:43.300
and simple living.

08:44.580 --> 08:47.130
Lord Yin managed such a palace,

08:47.130 --> 08:48.100
truly a model

08:48.940 --> 08:50.250
of household management.

08:52.380 --> 08:54.420
(Lotus and Moon)

09:07.610 --> 09:09.460
You two faced danger.

09:09.820 --> 09:11.490
I wanted to visit,

09:12.250 --> 09:13.420
but the sect was busy

09:13.420 --> 09:14.650
reorganizing defenses,

09:14.650 --> 09:15.700
checking disciples.

09:16.220 --> 09:17.580
I didn't have time.

09:18.130 --> 09:19.770
Today, I finally has a chance.

09:20.100 --> 09:22.490
This gift is a token of care

09:22.820 --> 09:23.980
to calm your nerves.

09:25.370 --> 09:26.420
Thank you for your concern.

09:27.130 --> 09:28.850
But we've done nothing.

09:29.370 --> 09:30.460
A gift is not needed.

09:39.340 --> 09:41.880
Your aunt and I bought this bracelet

09:41.890 --> 09:43.770
when traveling Jianghu.

09:43.850 --> 09:45.460
You can take it, right?

09:49.580 --> 09:50.460
Thank you, Lady Yin.

09:56.220 --> 09:57.060
Lingbo,

09:58.530 --> 10:01.490
Ms. Cai and I were like sisters.

10:01.730 --> 10:03.250
You and Zhao are fellow disciples.

10:04.100 --> 10:06.490
You should treat her well.

10:06.850 --> 10:08.340
It's hard to have such connections.

10:08.850 --> 10:09.690
Yes,

10:10.060 --> 10:10.980
Mother.

10:22.100 --> 10:22.980
Ning,

10:23.820 --> 10:25.650
I know your family has fine collections.

10:26.010 --> 10:28.300
Ordinary items might not impress you.

10:28.940 --> 10:29.850
Nanny Mao.

10:30.020 --> 10:30.870
Yes.

10:30.890 --> 10:31.770
Take Ning

10:31.770 --> 10:33.610
to the Treasure Vault

10:34.060 --> 10:35.460
and see if he likes anything.

10:35.820 --> 10:36.660
Yes.

10:57.940 --> 10:59.140
Have some tea.

11:00.370 --> 11:01.530
Thank you, Lady Yin.

11:19.180 --> 11:21.140
You have good taste.

11:21.650 --> 11:23.530
This jade was soaked in phoenix blood,

11:23.850 --> 11:25.060
extremely nourishing

11:25.340 --> 11:26.370
and precious.

11:27.180 --> 11:28.100
If you like it,

11:28.650 --> 11:30.060
you may take it.

11:32.370 --> 11:33.210
Madam,

11:34.060 --> 11:35.490
this was my family's property.

11:35.940 --> 11:37.850
I just want to bring it back.

11:39.340 --> 11:40.180
Mr. Chang,

11:40.420 --> 11:42.130
this is a treasured item of Madam.

11:42.130 --> 11:43.180
She can give it to you.

11:43.370 --> 11:44.730
How can it be taken back?

11:47.700 --> 11:48.610
Three years ago,

11:49.420 --> 11:51.060
my father fell ill

11:51.370 --> 11:52.283
due to Ms. Cai's death.

11:52.580 --> 11:54.940
Lord Qi let my father recuperate here.

11:55.490 --> 11:56.330
So,

11:56.530 --> 11:58.220
my father gave him this blood jade,

11:59.650 --> 12:02.100
but he overheard a quarrel
between you two.

12:03.220 --> 12:04.220
You said

12:04.650 --> 12:06.890
Cai Pingshu sacrificed herself
for the world,

12:07.060 --> 12:08.100
fighting Nie Hengcheng

12:08.100 --> 12:09.460
to mutual ruin.

12:10.629 --> 12:11.803
But that wretch dragged it out

12:12.250 --> 12:14.130
for over ten years before dying,

12:14.890 --> 12:16.010
truly detestable.

12:17.770 --> 12:19.010
My father was enraged,

12:19.180 --> 12:20.580
so he left here in sickness.

12:21.060 --> 12:22.100
Every time he recalled it,

12:23.420 --> 12:24.460
he was heartbroken.

12:25.100 --> 12:25.940
Chang Ning,

12:26.340 --> 12:28.010
we kindly took you in,

12:28.180 --> 12:29.580
yet you disobeyed.

12:29.580 --> 12:30.850
Now, you even slander my mother.

12:31.010 --> 12:32.060
Madam knows

12:33.300 --> 12:34.700
whether she had said that.

12:35.340 --> 12:36.180
Lady Yin,

12:37.610 --> 12:38.450
is this true?

12:40.580 --> 12:41.820
Of course not.

12:42.220 --> 12:43.580
Your family is despicable.

12:43.940 --> 12:46.220
You even drew thieves here.

12:46.730 --> 12:48.060
As a martial family,

12:48.239 --> 12:49.588
you collected wealth everywhere.

12:49.700 --> 12:51.460
Who knows what you hid

12:51.460 --> 12:52.730
to provoke the massacre?

12:53.180 --> 12:54.370
My father was fond of wealth

12:54.700 --> 12:55.850
but fair.

12:56.420 --> 12:57.460
He owed no one.

12:58.130 --> 12:59.180
The Yin family was greedy

12:59.477 --> 13:00.523
for wealth and reputation,

13:01.130 --> 13:03.490
which caused Ms. Cai's early death.

13:06.580 --> 13:08.650
Ning, you're slandering us.

13:09.060 --> 13:10.420
How disrespectful

13:10.420 --> 13:11.460
and impolite.

13:11.850 --> 13:13.300
Today, I'll teach you a lesson

13:13.300 --> 13:15.100
on behalf of the Lord.

13:15.820 --> 13:16.950
- Nanny Mao.
- Yes.

13:16.980 --> 13:17.820
Madam,

13:18.340 --> 13:20.130
Lingbo already lectured me

13:20.490 --> 13:21.770
openly and secretly.

13:22.700 --> 13:23.540
Could this be

13:24.580 --> 13:25.770
your instruction?

13:26.980 --> 13:28.130
Is today's kindness

13:28.420 --> 13:29.700
to win over Zhao,

13:30.060 --> 13:32.180
whom Lord Qi values,

13:32.420 --> 13:33.890
or out of guilt

13:34.650 --> 13:35.730
for Ms. Cai Pingshu?

13:36.010 --> 13:37.100
Nonsense.

13:37.170 --> 13:38.030
Guards!

13:38.040 --> 13:38.880
Yes.

13:39.500 --> 13:40.340
What are you doing?

13:40.340 --> 13:41.340
Seize Chang Ning.

13:41.560 --> 13:42.430
Yes.

13:42.460 --> 13:43.900
- You...
- Stop.

13:52.850 --> 13:53.690
Nanny Mao,

13:54.370 --> 13:55.230
what is this about?

13:55.250 --> 13:56.090
Milord.

13:56.180 --> 13:57.680
Father, Chang Ning...

14:04.580 --> 14:05.420
Dear,

14:06.580 --> 14:08.370
Ning is my guest.

14:09.180 --> 14:10.020
Besides,

14:10.370 --> 14:11.490
he is young,

14:11.850 --> 14:13.060
facing so much turmoil,

14:13.460 --> 14:15.980
so his emotions fluctuate.

14:16.650 --> 14:17.490
As an elder,

14:18.340 --> 14:19.980
you should show more tolerance.

14:24.370 --> 14:25.210
Ning,

14:26.010 --> 14:27.036
your wounds aren't healed.

14:27.300 --> 14:28.370
Go back

14:28.850 --> 14:30.130
and rest properly.

14:44.850 --> 14:45.970
- Master.
- Zhao.

14:47.100 --> 14:47.940
Come with me.

15:06.250 --> 15:07.090
Master,

15:07.250 --> 15:08.460
is what Chang Ning said true?

15:13.330 --> 15:14.770
Aunt went to kill Nie Hengcheng.

15:14.870 --> 15:16.100
What does that have to do

15:16.100 --> 15:17.370
with Lord Yin Dai?

15:23.112 --> 15:24.259
This is the Withered Branch.

15:25.180 --> 15:26.580
Your aunt brought it here.

15:31.100 --> 15:32.220
Withered Branch?

15:33.060 --> 15:34.066
I thought it was extinct.

15:34.613 --> 15:35.850
I came from a humble background.

15:36.420 --> 15:37.260
Back then,

15:37.460 --> 15:38.490
I was just

15:38.490 --> 15:40.250
an unremarkable outer disciple,

15:40.890 --> 15:43.180
often bullied by senior brothers.

15:53.900 --> 15:57.180
(Young Qi Yunke, Qingque Sect)

15:58.060 --> 16:00.300
Until that day, Pingshu appeared

16:01.010 --> 16:02.130
and rescued me.

16:03.100 --> 16:04.180
Pingshu told me

16:04.700 --> 16:06.126
that I have the Tianhuo Dragon Bone,

16:06.556 --> 16:07.610
that once I break through,

16:07.610 --> 16:08.980
I can soar,

16:09.820 --> 16:12.250
and that I must not give up

16:12.313 --> 16:13.299
because of early failure.

16:22.700 --> 16:24.340
Under her guidance,

16:25.130 --> 16:26.890
I got the Tianhuo Dragon Meridian,

16:27.340 --> 16:28.180
becoming a disciple

16:28.530 --> 16:29.980
of Lord Yin.

16:31.100 --> 16:32.580
To strengthen my inner power,

16:32.940 --> 16:34.460
she found the Withered Branch.

16:35.180 --> 16:36.220
Once it blooms,

16:36.577 --> 16:37.597
it can be used as medicine

16:38.420 --> 16:40.370
to aid my cultivation.

16:45.650 --> 16:47.420
But before it bloomed,

16:48.370 --> 16:49.940
Nie Hengcheng

16:50.100 --> 16:51.460
completed his dark arts,

16:51.700 --> 16:54.340
devastating the Six Sects,

16:54.420 --> 16:55.460
and killing countless.

16:59.420 --> 17:00.850
I should have realized.

17:01.890 --> 17:04.180
Pingshu was always ahead of us,

17:05.220 --> 17:06.330
never letting us

17:06.490 --> 17:07.730
die with her.

17:12.700 --> 17:14.380
Whenever I think of my aunt

17:14.620 --> 17:15.900
covered in blood,

17:16.700 --> 17:18.420
barely alive,

17:20.290 --> 17:21.940
I feel anger and sorrow.

17:24.980 --> 17:26.090
If only someone had been

17:27.090 --> 17:28.420
with her at the time,

17:30.090 --> 17:32.810
even just to assist.

17:35.660 --> 17:37.090
This is Jianghu:

17:38.810 --> 17:39.900
Heroic ones

17:40.730 --> 17:41.900
risk their lives,

17:43.700 --> 17:45.220
yet good endings are not guaranteed.

17:58.140 --> 17:59.530
I've long stopped

18:00.700 --> 18:01.700
believing in karma.

18:05.730 --> 18:07.530
That's why I said I don't like Jianghu.

18:07.690 --> 18:09.250
Yet you and my parents insisted I come.

18:14.490 --> 18:15.900
You don't need to enter Jianghu,

18:17.730 --> 18:19.050
but you must become powerful.

18:20.010 --> 18:20.850
Only then

18:20.980 --> 18:22.140
can you live without worry.

18:24.570 --> 18:26.250
Your aunt wanted you to learn from me

18:26.730 --> 18:27.860
because she wanted you

18:28.140 --> 18:30.090
to diligently practice

18:30.366 --> 18:31.586
and refine your martial skills.

18:32.570 --> 18:33.570
In life,

18:34.180 --> 18:36.660
there are times beyond one's control.

18:37.050 --> 18:38.730
Only by becoming strong

18:39.380 --> 18:40.380
can one be free.

18:41.810 --> 18:42.650
Back then,

18:43.010 --> 18:44.250
no matter what others said,

18:44.860 --> 18:47.330
your aunt acted as she wished.

18:49.940 --> 18:50.900
I hope

18:53.090 --> 18:54.250
you can do the same.

18:55.010 --> 18:56.050
Stand for justice

18:56.330 --> 18:57.570
in the martial world,

18:57.770 --> 18:59.062
act chivalrously,

18:59.073 --> 19:00.519
oppose the strong, and aid the weak,

19:00.530 --> 19:02.380
so that grievances are addressed,

19:02.380 --> 19:04.330
and everyone can achieve something.

19:29.980 --> 19:30.820
(Trace Butterflies.)

19:56.810 --> 19:57.650
Zhao, you're back.

19:58.420 --> 20:00.090
(He lured the butterflies here?)

20:27.860 --> 20:29.050
Ning, why are you here,

20:30.010 --> 20:32.620
and why did you attract
so many Trace Butterflies?

20:32.940 --> 20:33.940
Father has regretted

20:34.706 --> 20:36.086
that during the Battle of Mount Tu,

20:36.570 --> 20:37.530
he was a step too late

20:38.460 --> 20:40.050
and could not fight with Ms. Cai.

20:41.620 --> 20:43.860
Over the years, he tried many ways

20:44.420 --> 20:46.330
and finally found Qiong pollen

20:46.530 --> 20:47.570
to attract the butterflies,

20:48.890 --> 20:50.123
but Ms. Cai had already passed.

20:55.180 --> 20:56.020
This is for you.

21:01.840 --> 21:07.390
♪But I can't forget your face♪

21:07.930 --> 21:11.640
♪Life♪

21:11.650 --> 21:14.070
♪Passes swiftly♪

21:14.860 --> 21:16.750
♪Time is long♪

21:16.760 --> 21:18.500
♪Pleasures are few♪

21:19.530 --> 21:21.460
You deliberately mention my aunt today,

21:21.860 --> 21:22.940
risking offending Lady Yin,

21:23.290 --> 21:24.380
to stir conflict between us.

21:25.180 --> 21:26.730
Now, you use these butterflies

21:26.730 --> 21:28.050
to make me recall past emotions.

21:28.940 --> 21:30.010
What exactly do you want?

21:30.380 --> 21:31.810
♪In the end♪

21:32.420 --> 21:34.620
I can't tell
if those around me are good.

21:36.250 --> 21:37.220
I only trust you.

21:39.250 --> 21:40.620
I want to remind you

21:41.660 --> 21:43.050
not to easily trust others.

21:43.580 --> 21:44.930
♪Liquor is strong♪

21:44.940 --> 21:47.140
I also hope you'll protect me

21:47.770 --> 21:49.050
for the sake of the bond

21:49.553 --> 21:50.746
between Ms. Cai and my father.

21:53.050 --> 21:54.860
How do you want me to protect you?

21:57.340 --> 22:00.830
♪Leaving only me♪

22:01.490 --> 22:03.010
I'm still poisoned.

22:03.620 --> 22:05.980
Uncle Lei told me to go
to recover at Herb Hut.

22:06.570 --> 22:07.700
I wonder

22:08.090 --> 22:09.010
if you'd accompany me.

22:11.330 --> 22:12.170
(Uncle Lei?)

22:16.220 --> 22:17.660
Lei Xiuming

22:17.660 --> 22:19.490
is praised by thousands.

22:20.140 --> 22:21.810
He's the most beautiful man

22:21.810 --> 22:23.490
in Jianghu.

22:23.490 --> 22:24.460
(Herb Hut)

22:24.460 --> 22:25.730
Pink in spring,

22:25.980 --> 22:27.460
blue in summer,

22:27.940 --> 22:29.490
yellow in autumn,

22:29.490 --> 22:30.860
and white in winter.

22:30.860 --> 22:33.460
He dresses better than the girls.

22:49.140 --> 22:50.700
(Lei Xiuming, Qingque Sect)

22:50.700 --> 22:52.180
I must look differently

22:52.273 --> 22:53.246
from what your aunt said.

22:54.490 --> 22:56.140
She rarely mentioned Qingque Sect

22:56.700 --> 22:58.220
but often spoke of you

22:58.530 --> 22:59.940
and Uncle Guo.

23:00.330 --> 23:01.170
They're gone.

23:04.180 --> 23:05.420
Only I, an invalid,

23:06.730 --> 23:07.620
struggle to survive.

23:08.460 --> 23:09.380
Past events

23:09.956 --> 23:11.110
are better left unmentioned.

23:14.490 --> 23:16.700
Uncle Lei, you are in the top three

23:16.700 --> 23:18.090
on the Celebrity List.

23:19.180 --> 23:21.090
They say you are

23:21.220 --> 23:22.290
the greatest healer.

23:22.570 --> 23:24.700
All heroes respect you.

23:32.420 --> 23:33.260
Master.

23:34.250 --> 23:35.620
Xingjia is ready.

23:36.090 --> 23:36.930
Let's go.

23:41.660 --> 23:42.620
Jueyinshu acupoint,

23:42.960 --> 23:43.830
half a cun.

23:43.860 --> 23:44.700
Uncle Lei,

23:45.380 --> 23:46.770
that is a fatal acupoint.

23:47.420 --> 23:48.380
Seeking life in death.

23:48.860 --> 23:49.860
A risky medical move.

23:50.460 --> 23:51.300
Uncle Lei, brilliant.

23:58.530 --> 23:59.370
Zhao.

24:08.250 --> 24:09.090
Ning,

24:09.730 --> 24:11.180
I'm just an amateur.

24:11.570 --> 24:12.620
If I make a mistake,

24:13.380 --> 24:14.420
don't blame me.

24:14.810 --> 24:15.650
It's fine.

24:16.330 --> 24:17.420
Only half a life at risk.

24:18.660 --> 24:19.500
Zhao,

24:20.050 --> 24:20.890
don't worry.

24:41.330 --> 24:42.980
(Irregular pulse.)

24:43.250 --> 24:44.570
(Hidden old poison.)

24:52.010 --> 24:54.290
You risked your life
on the cliff to protect me

24:55.140 --> 24:56.420
and helped remove my poison.

24:57.290 --> 24:58.130
I'm truly grateful.

25:00.660 --> 25:02.770
I heard you were sickly as a child.

25:03.490 --> 25:04.900
Uncle Chang took great care,

25:05.220 --> 25:06.810
so you never left Chang Fort.

25:07.692 --> 25:09.046
But that night, during the attack,

25:09.620 --> 25:11.420
I saw your agile moves.

25:11.810 --> 25:13.140
During the acupuncture session,

25:13.250 --> 25:14.980
I sensed your immense

25:15.420 --> 25:16.606
and extraordinary inner power.

25:18.900 --> 25:20.090
Since I recovered at ten,

25:21.369 --> 25:23.175
my father often passed on
inner power to me.

25:23.980 --> 25:25.050
Uncles in the fort

25:25.366 --> 25:26.812
also taught me everything they knew.

25:28.530 --> 25:30.220
You have such skill

25:30.220 --> 25:31.460
before reaching adulthood.

25:31.900 --> 25:33.330
How gifted.

25:34.180 --> 25:35.286
What about this old poison?

25:36.330 --> 25:37.330
Where did it come from?

25:39.330 --> 25:40.490
I was weak since childhood.

25:42.010 --> 25:44.330
My father once used
a counter-poison method

25:46.090 --> 25:47.220
to help me survive.

25:48.140 --> 25:50.420
If it can ease your doubts,

25:51.660 --> 25:53.380
I can write the formula for you.

26:20.250 --> 26:21.770
Ning, how do you feel?

26:25.730 --> 26:26.570
Let's go back.

26:35.490 --> 26:36.330
Zhao,

26:36.660 --> 26:38.330
there seems to be poison in the water.

26:43.770 --> 26:44.730
Chang Ning!

27:07.330 --> 27:08.460
Zhao, what's wrong?

27:11.010 --> 27:12.460
You're fair-skinned and handsome,

27:13.250 --> 27:14.530
refined and noble,

27:15.420 --> 27:17.140
nothing like Uncle Chang.

27:19.570 --> 27:20.460
Zhao,

27:21.770 --> 27:22.940
have you ever seen my mother?

28:01.220 --> 28:02.060
Take medicine.

28:13.730 --> 28:14.570
What's this?

28:15.530 --> 28:16.370
Smiley.

28:16.810 --> 28:17.810
My aunt taught me,

28:18.090 --> 28:19.180
hoping whoever eats it

28:19.530 --> 28:20.660
will be happy.

28:31.330 --> 28:32.170
So sweet.

28:36.860 --> 28:38.220
Since you are fine now,

28:39.860 --> 28:40.700
please go back.

28:44.180 --> 28:45.020
Zhao,

28:45.980 --> 28:47.490
may I stay for a few days?

28:48.010 --> 28:49.090
When my wounds heal,

28:49.527 --> 28:50.687
I'll return to Peace Chamber.

28:53.490 --> 28:54.700
My poison isn't cleared;

28:56.490 --> 28:58.460
someone tampered with the herbal bath.

28:59.220 --> 29:00.980
You can't just watch me die.

29:32.050 --> 29:33.050
My purple jade inkstone!

29:33.180 --> 29:34.180
Don't come near me.

29:34.460 --> 29:35.570
I'll kill you.

29:35.730 --> 29:37.290
The effect is so strong?

29:37.770 --> 29:38.770
You are a murderer!

29:38.770 --> 29:39.610
Oh, my goodness.

29:40.250 --> 29:42.290
I only added a little Truth Teller
in the medicine.

29:44.140 --> 29:45.010
Die!

29:46.940 --> 29:47.780
Chang Ning.

29:47.940 --> 29:48.780
Chang Ning,

29:48.790 --> 29:49.630
wake up!

29:49.640 --> 29:50.520
Don't come near.

29:50.700 --> 29:51.810
You killed my father!

29:52.140 --> 29:53.620
You killed my father!

29:54.940 --> 29:56.250
He really is Uncle Chang's son.

29:56.290 --> 29:57.140
I'll kill you!

29:57.220 --> 29:58.610
Chang Ning, wake up!

30:00.330 --> 30:01.290
You killed my father!

30:01.810 --> 30:02.860
I'll kill you!

30:03.940 --> 30:04.860
I'll kill you!

30:07.250 --> 30:08.090
Oh, no.

30:08.120 --> 30:09.360
He really thinks I'm his enemy.

30:13.220 --> 30:14.060
Have you heard?

30:14.530 --> 30:16.220
Chang Ning moved into Chunling Cottage.

30:16.330 --> 30:17.860
They're living together.

30:18.250 --> 30:19.420
How improper!

30:20.700 --> 30:21.540
Zhao, be careful.

30:41.140 --> 30:42.700
- Let's go.
- Go!

30:43.580 --> 30:45.460
(Glow of Moonlight and Flowers)

30:47.813 --> 30:49.013
Osmanthus and angelica congee.

30:49.290 --> 30:50.563
It calms the mind, regulates qi,

30:51.010 --> 30:51.940
and helps

30:51.940 --> 30:52.810
with staying up late

30:53.250 --> 30:54.090
and headaches.

30:58.290 --> 30:59.770
Last night, I sleepwalked.

31:00.380 --> 31:01.490
I hope I didn't break

31:01.490 --> 31:02.770
anything of yours.

31:04.620 --> 31:05.700
It's fine.

31:05.940 --> 31:07.410
It's understandable for sleepwalking.

31:07.770 --> 31:08.610
I won't mind.

31:10.090 --> 31:12.010
You helped me several times,

31:13.090 --> 31:14.050
gave me sweet congee,

31:14.700 --> 31:15.773
and generously let me stay.

31:16.490 --> 31:17.636
I must reward you handsomely.

31:20.820 --> 31:21.670
Ning,

31:21.700 --> 31:23.090
are you rich?

31:24.249 --> 31:25.495
Father had considerable savings.

31:25.770 --> 31:27.050
Not many rare medicine formulas.

31:27.660 --> 31:30.570
But treasures and money

31:30.940 --> 31:32.770
are hidden in places that only I know.

31:33.180 --> 31:34.460
So, you are rich.

31:34.980 --> 31:35.820
Not really.

31:36.980 --> 31:38.290
But if you protect me

31:38.770 --> 31:40.490
in Qingque Sect,

31:40.903 --> 31:42.096
after going down the mountain,

31:42.730 --> 31:44.123
I'm willing to give all my wealth.

31:45.420 --> 31:46.260
All of it?

31:46.700 --> 31:47.540
Yes.

31:47.810 --> 31:48.650
A gentleman's word?

31:48.940 --> 31:49.780
Hard to retract.

31:49.980 --> 31:50.820
Then it's settled.

31:51.010 --> 31:52.050
I'll protect you.

31:52.220 --> 31:53.350
- Eat up.
- Thanks.

32:03.126 --> 32:04.192
Your gesture is wrong here.

32:04.460 --> 32:05.460
Bend it more,

32:06.570 --> 32:07.420
open this side,

32:08.810 --> 32:09.976
and apply force in your palm.

32:11.513 --> 32:12.889
The mindful way of Luoying Valley

32:12.900 --> 32:14.530
will help your wound heal sooner.

32:15.140 --> 32:16.260
I was sickly in childhood.

32:16.330 --> 32:17.180
It also helped me.

32:17.860 --> 32:19.270
- Again.
- Okay.

32:19.290 --> 32:20.570
Living in the same chamber,

32:20.570 --> 32:22.180
young and affectionate.

32:22.460 --> 32:23.810
How friendly.

32:24.530 --> 32:27.050
Why are you two here?

32:27.250 --> 32:29.940
Chang has moved here.

32:30.380 --> 32:31.220
Why?

32:31.530 --> 32:32.700
Can't we come?

32:45.980 --> 32:46.860
Just so-so.

32:47.620 --> 32:48.530
I heard

32:49.380 --> 32:50.530
that last night,

32:50.700 --> 32:52.050
you and he

32:52.530 --> 32:53.380
were quite noisy.

32:54.570 --> 32:56.090
Noisy?

32:57.810 --> 32:58.730
More than that.

32:59.810 --> 33:02.050
We were earth-shattering.

33:03.220 --> 33:06.330
My sister and Ning were sparring.

33:06.330 --> 33:07.980
Sparring?

33:09.620 --> 33:10.460
Zhao,

33:10.900 --> 33:12.490
if others hear that you

33:12.940 --> 33:14.050
spent the night together,

33:14.330 --> 33:15.730
it will spread rumors.

33:17.460 --> 33:19.700
Let it spread.

33:20.010 --> 33:22.390
It won't cost me any money, right?

33:22.420 --> 33:23.380
No.

33:23.770 --> 33:25.290
What on earth are you two up to?

33:25.570 --> 33:26.900
That's our secret.

33:27.620 --> 33:29.140
We can't tell you.

33:29.940 --> 33:31.180
It's already autumn.

33:35.290 --> 33:37.250
Why are toads still croaking?

33:39.860 --> 33:40.656
Ning,

33:40.667 --> 33:42.010
your injuries haven't healed yet.

33:42.810 --> 33:44.050
Let's rest first.

33:46.460 --> 33:47.530
Stop right there!

33:48.730 --> 33:49.900
- Lingbo.
- What?

33:50.090 --> 33:51.140
Master repeatedly said

33:51.290 --> 33:52.460
no more conflicts with them.

33:52.900 --> 33:55.250
Ribbit, ribbit, ribbit.

33:56.050 --> 33:57.570
I'm too lazy to argue with them.

33:58.530 --> 33:59.370
Lingbo.

34:00.420 --> 34:01.620
Didn't you say

34:02.250 --> 34:03.276
that peace brings wealth?

34:04.140 --> 34:05.090
Why provoke her?

34:05.090 --> 34:06.140
I don't want trouble,

34:06.973 --> 34:08.233
but I'm not afraid of it either.

34:08.690 --> 34:10.420
For those who stir conflict,

34:10.650 --> 34:11.740
you must not indulge them.

34:16.820 --> 34:18.860
This is family heritage.

34:19.740 --> 34:21.940
Her grandfather, Yin Dai,
relied on words alone

34:22.460 --> 34:25.210
to send your aunt to kill the demon.

34:25.690 --> 34:27.940
Why are you sowing discord again?

34:30.340 --> 34:31.420
To approach me,

34:31.940 --> 34:34.130
you even tampered with the herbal bath

34:34.420 --> 34:35.860
and moved here.

34:37.090 --> 34:38.130
What exactly do you want?

34:38.530 --> 34:39.370
Or,

34:40.420 --> 34:41.473
what do you want me to do?

34:45.300 --> 34:46.690
You're truly clever.

34:47.980 --> 34:49.210
I did all this

34:49.860 --> 34:51.780
just to show you the truth.

34:52.820 --> 34:54.460
The one who pushed your aunt

34:54.980 --> 34:56.650
to kill the demon alone

34:56.980 --> 34:58.090
was Lord Yin.

34:59.010 --> 35:00.420
If you don't believe me,

35:00.740 --> 35:02.650
you can check the secret room
in the Library.

35:03.300 --> 35:04.420
I heard

35:05.050 --> 35:07.300
every lord has a handbook.

35:08.340 --> 35:09.820
There must be

35:09.820 --> 35:11.010
some clues in it.

35:11.610 --> 35:12.460
Library?

35:20.220 --> 35:23.820
(Library)

35:41.940 --> 35:43.050
Xuanji Array.

36:03.980 --> 36:07.100
(Pillar of Righteousness)

36:31.740 --> 36:32.580
(6th)

36:32.580 --> 36:35.460
(11th)
(Master is the 20th lord.)

36:36.300 --> 36:38.820
(18th)
(Yin Dai should be 19th.)

36:53.170 --> 36:54.340
Ning?

36:56.170 --> 36:57.340
What are you doing here?

36:57.650 --> 36:58.490
To return the favor,

36:59.380 --> 37:00.530
I'm here to search

37:00.940 --> 37:01.860
for the truth with you.

37:07.321 --> 37:17.981
=Generation to Generation=

37:36.741 --> 37:41.151
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

37:41.716 --> 37:46.331
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

37:46.671 --> 37:51.236
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

37:51.761 --> 37:56.061
♪Free to wander in the world♪

37:59.006 --> 38:03.706
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:04.231 --> 38:08.521
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

38:09.181 --> 38:13.211
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

38:13.526 --> 38:18.651
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

38:19.226 --> 38:24.036
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:24.251 --> 38:28.421
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:29.146 --> 38:33.081
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:33.581 --> 38:38.856
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

39:01.586 --> 39:06.716
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:07.081 --> 39:11.451
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:11.716 --> 39:15.846
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:16.031 --> 39:21.606
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
